The End Of Times Burger (Clasic Garbage)
This is my first collection of 3 unique pieces (three hamburgers) with limited editions.

The Classic Burger represents the absurdity of the world system, becoming each person responsible for the disaster that we live on the planet.

Inequality, Laziness, Indolence, Greed, Corruption ...
The post-apocalyptic world is today ...
